articles.title: Lionel Messi, David Beckham and Sergio Busquets enjoy dinner with their wives at Bad Bunny's Miami steakhouse - Daily Mail
articles.description: The World Cup winner has made an impressive start to his Inter Miami career but appears to be enjoying life off the pitch as much as he is on it as Victoria Beckham shared photos of the Messis and Beckhams.
articles.content:
Lionel Messi continued enjoying his start to life in Miami as he enjoyed dinner with Inter Miami co-owner David Beckham and his wife Victoria.
